### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Get all teachers
GET {{apiUrl}}/teachers
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get teacher by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/teachers/001
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get teacher by ID (Not Found)
GET {{apiUrl}}/teachers/999
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new teacher
POST {{apiUrl}}/teachers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "magv": "011",
  "hoTen": "Lê Văn Nam",
  "luong": 2200,
  "phai": "Nam",
  "ngSinh": "1985-05-15",
  "diaChi": "50 Nguyễn Thị Minh Khai, Q.3, TP HCM",
  "mabm": "HTTT"
}

###

### Update teacher
PUT {{apiUrl}}/teachers/001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "luong": 2500,
  "diaChi": "25/3 Lạc Long Quân, Q.10, TP HCM (Updated)"
}

###

### Update teacher (Not Found)
PUT {{apiUrl}}/teachers/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "luong": 3000
}

###

### Delete teacher
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/teachers/011
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Delete teacher (Not Found)
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/teachers/999
Content-Type: application/json

